'''''Sankofa'''''  ni filime yerekana ikinamico yakozwe [[Etiyopiya|na Etiyopiya yo mu]] 1993 iyobowe na Haile Gerima yibanze ku bucuruzi bw’abacakara bwa Atlantike . Iyi nkuru igaragaramo Oyafunmike Ogunlano, Kofi Ghanaba, Mutabaruka, Alexandra Duah, na Afemo Omilami . Ijambo Sankofa ryakomotse ku rurimi rwa Akan rwo [[Gana|muri Gana]] risobanura "gusubira inyuma, gushaka, no kubona ubwenge, imbaraga n'ibyiringiro", nk'uko byavuzwe na Dr. Anna Julia Cooper.  Ijambo Sankofa ryibanda ku kamaro ko umuntu atagendera kure cyane ya kahise kugirango atere imbere ejo hazaza. Muri filime, Sankofa agereranwa ninyoni n'indirimbo n'ingoma z'ingoma y'Imana.  Filime ya Gerima yerekanye akamaro ko kutagira abantu bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] batandukana n’imizi yabo. Gerima yakoresheje urugendo rwimico Mona kugirango yerekane uburyo imyumvire nyafurika yerekana indangamuntu harimo kumenya imizi yumuntu no "gusubira aho yaturutse" (Gerima).

== Umugambi ==
Filime itangirana numusaza Divine Drummer , Sankofa (yakinnye na Kofi Ghanaba ), akubita ingoma nyafurika aririmba imvugo ngo "Umwuka utinda w'abapfuye, haguruka." Ubu ni uburyo bwe bwo gushyikirana nabakurambere b'igihugu cya [[Afrika]],  cyane [[Gana]]. Yizera ko kuvuza ingoma ari ngombwa mu kugarura umwuka w'abakurambere be biciwe muri diaspora nyafurika .  Inkuru ikomeza kugaragaza Mona (Oyafunmike Ogunlano), wabayeho Afurika na Amerika ntangarugero kuri film shoot muri [[Gana|Ghana]] . Afite isomo ku Kigo cya Cape Coast, atazi ko cyakoreshejwe mu mateka mu bucuruzi bw’abacakara   kubera ko kuva kera atandukanijwe n’imizi [[Afurika|ye yo muri Afurika.]] Mugihe Mona ari kumurongo wicyitegererezo, ahura numusaza wamayobera Sankofa wavuzaga ingoma mugutangira film. Sankofa akomeje kwibutsa Mona gusubira mu mateka ye kandi akaba umunyamahane cyane mu bijyanye no gukomeza ahantu h'abasekuruza bera, bityo agerageza kwirukana ba mukerarugendo b'abazungu mu kigo cy'abacakara.  Iyo Mona ingingo kujya A Kureba imbere castle ubwe,  Mona agerageza guhunga urugo rw'abacakara ahura na ba shebuja b'abaja bera agerageza gutekereza avuga ko akomoka muri [[Amerika]] kandi ko adakomoka muri [[Afurika]] . Ba shebuja b'abacakara ntibitaye ku byo Mona yavuze maze bamusunika ku muriro, bamwambura imyenda, bamushyira icyuma gishyushye ku mugongo.

